            . On the 5th of this instant, between six and seven in the evening, the prisoner had entered a house in the Strand, and got up stairs, and I took him, and before Sir 
               <persName id="t17700425-27-person363">
                  John
                   Fielding
               <interp inst="t17700425-27-person363" type="surname" value="Fielding"></interp>
