                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17700425-27-defend358 t17700425-27-deflabel159"></join>. He has been gone from me upwards of two years. I can give no account how he has lived since.</p>
               <p>Q. How did he behave while with you?</p>
               <p>E. Bateman. I dismissed him from my service two or three times.</p>
